alright, more proper introduction now that i’ve got this bad boy more organized!

my favorite pokemon changes a lot and bayleef (and its evolutions) are some current favorites, so i was surprised one of these didn’t exist for bayleef already, so, naturally, i went ahead and decided to make it a reality!

mostly gonna be reblogs and i’ll probably keep stuff running on a queue and as long as i can find bayleef content then i’ll reblog it!

so, any and all lovers of bayleef are welcome, and i hope people enjoy!
